'''帕特里夏·阿奎特'''（{{lang-en|Patricia Arquette}}，{{bd|1968年|4月8日}}）是一位[[美國|美國]][[女演員|女演員]]。2005年起在電視劇《[[靈媒緝凶|靈媒緝凶]]》中演出身為[[靈媒|靈媒]]的主人翁，亦屢次憑此角入圍[[金球獎_(影視獎項)|金球獎]]、[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]及[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]，更因此角色於2005年获[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]。憑藉《[[年少時代|年少時代]]》中母親的角色獲得多項電影獎，包括包括[[美國演員工會獎最佳女配角|美國演員工會獎最佳女配角]]、[[英國電影學院獎最佳女配角|英國電影學院獎最佳女配角]]和[[第72届金球奖|第72届金球奖]]戲劇最佳女配角以及[[第87屆奧斯卡金像獎|第87届奥斯卡金像奖]]最佳女配角等獎項。

==家庭及私人生活==
=== 家人 ===

派翠西亞·艾奎特的母親Brenda Denaut是[[猶太人|猶太人]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/10937835/Patricia-Arquette-interview-on-Boyhood-Nicolas-Cage-and-growing-up.html|title=Patricia Arquette interview: on Boyhood, Nicolas Cage and growing up|last=Bussmann|first=Kate|date=February 9, 2015|work=The Telegraph|accessdate=May 23, 2018|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121081027/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/10937835/Patricia-Arquette-interview-on-Boyhood-Nicolas-Cage-and-growing-up.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/patricia-arquette-the-not-so-dippy-hippie-412274.html|title=Patricia Arquette: The not-so-dippy hippie|last=Hoggard|first=Liz|date=August 18, 2006|work=The Independent|accessdate=May 23, 2018|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610141423/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/patricia-arquette-the-not-so-dippy-hippie-412274.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/patricia-arquettes-early-life-on-a-virginia-commune-1513096040|title=Patricia Arquette’s Early Life on a Virginia Commune|date=December 12, 2017|work=Wall Street Journal|accessdate=May 23, 2018|quote=Patricia Arquette: "My mom was Jewish"|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109042333/https://www.wsj.com/articles/patricia-arquettes-early-life-on-a-virginia-commune-1513096040|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.mystatesman.com/lifestyles/arquette-prepares-passionate-plea-for-equality-austin-event/FE5z7yi73ozvUaVCM9RR8K/|title=Arquette prepares a passionate plea for equality at Austin event|last=Sumner|first=Jane|date=October 10, 2015|work=Austin American-Statesman|accessdate=May 23, 2018|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622165039/https://www.mystatesman.com/lifestyles/arquette-prepares-passionate-plea-for-equality-austin-event/FE5z7yi73ozvUaVCM9RR8K/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。派翠西亞·艾奎特的外祖父是[[猶太人大屠殺|猶太人大屠殺]]的倖存者<ref>{{cite news|url=http://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/6855/|title=Arquette Reconnects|last=Pfefferman|first=Naomi|date=October 17, 2002|work=The Jewish Journal of Greater Los Angeles|accessdate=May 24, 2018|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629041248/https://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/6855/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。派翠西亞·艾奎特的父親Lewis Arquette有英格蘭、[[法裔加拿大人|法裔加拿大人]]、瑞士德國人、蘇格蘭、德國、愛爾蘭和威爾士血統<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000099/bio|title=Patricia Arquette - Biography|accessdate=|author=|date=|work=IMDb|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104013116/https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000099/bio|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

父親Lewis Arquette是演員<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2001/feb/13/local/me-24843|title=Lewis Arquette; Actor, Comic Continued Family Trade|last=Oliver|first=Myrna|date=February 13, 2001|work=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=May 23, 2018|archive-date=2014-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140911224549/http://articles.latimes.com/2001/feb/13/local/me-24843|dead-url=no}}</ref>。祖父Cliff Arquette也是演員<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":0" />。曾祖父母是[[歌舞雜耍表演|歌舞雜耍表演]]演員<ref name=":2">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1995/08/20/movies/none-of-that-sultry-innocence-for-a-change.html|title=None of That Sultry Innocence For a Change|last=Smith|first=Dinitia|date=August 20, 1995|work=The New York Times|accessdate=May 24, 2018|archive-date=2020-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224091007/https://www.nytimes.com/1995/08/20/movies/none-of-that-sultry-innocence-for-a-change.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。父親是[[梅里韦瑟·刘易斯|梅里韦瑟·刘易斯]]的後裔<ref name=":1" />。

幾名兄弟姊妹均在演藝界發展，包括[[羅珊娜·艾奎特|羅珊娜·艾奎特]]及[[大衛·艾奎特|大衛·艾奎特]]（David Arquette）<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/david-arquette-bar-mitzvah-trip-israel-tweets-finally-man-article-1.1093601|title=David Arquette has bar mitzvah during first trip to Israel, tweets: ‘Finally I’m a man’|date=June 11, 2012|work=New York Daily News|accessdate=May 23, 2018|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924012744/https://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/david-arquette-bar-mitzvah-trip-israel-tweets-finally-man-article-1.1093601|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亦因[[大衛·艾奎特|大衛·艾奎特]]娶了[[柯特妮·考克斯|柯特妮·考克斯]]的關係而成為考克斯的大姑子。

兒子Enzo在1989年出生，兒子的父親是前男友[[Paul_Rossi|Paul Rossi]]；女兒在2003年出生，女兒的父親是前夫[[Thomas_Jane|Thomas Jane]]。

=== 婚姻 ===
於1995年4月8日，在她滿27歲生日當天与电影演员[[尼古拉斯·凯奇|尼古拉斯·凯奇]]成婚，2000年离异。2006年6月25日與[[湯馬士·珍|湯馬士·珍]]結婚，2010年離異。

